{"arkId":"cl010099489","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099489","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre octogonale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre octogonale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri IV (1589-1610) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1615","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1615,"imprecision":"","text":"D\u00e9but du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7056","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre octogonale, bo\u00eetier grav\u00e9 \u00e0 pans coup\u00e9s. Sur la carrure, au centre du couvercle et du fond, des plaques ont \u00e9t\u00e9 rapport\u00e9es ; m\u00e9daillon central du fond repr\u00e9sentant l\u0027Enl\u00e8vement de Ganym\u00e8de d\u0027apr\u00e8s une estampe d\u0027E. Delaune ; celui du cadran figurant Diane d\u00e9couvrant la grossesse de Callisto d\u0027apr\u00e8s une gravure de Th\u00e9odore de Bry. Huit pans encadrant chacune des sc\u00e8nes grav\u00e9s d\u0027animaux courant et de rinceaux. Carrure grav\u00e9e de rinceaux fleuris, d\u0027un \u00e9cureuil, un lapin, une femme et un homme couch\u00e9s. Pendant en forme de chapiteau. Cadran octogonal grav\u00e9 de rinceaux et fleurettes, d\u0027un guerrier couch\u00e9 et d\u0027un lapin.. A l\u0027int\u00e9rieur de l\u0027anneau horaire, \u00e0 chiffres romains, apparait une vue de ville. Ajust\u00e9 dans le bo\u00eetier, mouvement dot\u00e9 d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 verge, une fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq et cliquet grav\u00e9s et ajour\u00e9s de rinceaux fleuris. Les platines ont un contour form\u00e9 de six lobes.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"6,4","displayDimension":"6,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3,5","displayDimension":"3,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,2","displayDimension":"2,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"France (Europe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Gavet ; collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri IV (1589-1610)"}],"place":[{"value":"France"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Rohou, Julie (dir.), Graver la Renaissance : Etienne Delaune et les arts d\u00e9coratifs, cat. exp. (Ecouen (Externe, France), Mus\u00e9e de la Renaissance - ch\u00e2teau d\u0027Ecouen, 16 octobre 2019 - 3 f\u00e9vrier 2020), Paris, R\u00e9union des mus\u00e9es nationaux-Grand Palais, 2019","bibliographyDate":"2019","bibliographyDetail":"p. 148-149, n\u00b0 59","com